      "rationale": "All model inputs are characterised with documented sources and uncertainty bounds. The blood viscosity rheological parameter uncertainty is wide (95% CI spans a factor of ~1.7 on k) due to inter-study biological variability; this is an inherent limitation of in-vitro blood analogue data. The sensitivity analysis demonstrates that despite this uncertainty, the rank-ordering of worst-case operating conditions is robust across the full parameter range. Gradation 2 achieved with explicit uncertainty documentation."
